{"tid":884827,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"「開源」點解買oneplus 6T? 廠方3日就釋出了op6內核原始碼！","createTime":"2018-11-01T02:00:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T16:48:28.000Z","uid":12628,"like":12,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"81042a5218e5b19e229611e3a2db26f89cf28d3f","tid":884827,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pgq8atc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgq8atc.png&h=9ce09650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前 OnePlus 6T 在紐約正式發佈，以更簡潔設計及更長的電池續航力，加上6.41 吋水滴全屏，及採用屏下指紋技術。規格方面配備 Snapdragon 845 八核處理器，最高 8GB RAM + 256GB ROM，內置3700mAh 電池，後置鏡頭為1600 + 2000 萬像素雙鏡頭。規格及設計方面都是一般主流的設計，然而有朋友疑惑 OnePlus 是內地大陸手機，問及為何還會受到外國用戶的歡迎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nRGfzUO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRGfzUO.png&h=d33a2778&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實是有原因的，<span style=\"color: red;\">其中一個原因就是在推出不到三日， OnePlus 就公佈並釋出了 OnePlus 6T 的內核原始碼。雖然根據開源協議是需要釋出的，然而一樣有內地廠商沒有公開。</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">一加手機的用戶，是一堆喜歡DIY系統及手機硬件的資深玩家，</span>特別是用 OnePlus 作系統及軟件開發的測試裝置之用。這些用戶對系統的內核原始碼最熟悉不過， 而 Oneplus 手機正會吸引這些用戶購買，長久便累積這一用戶群。如果對 OnePlus 6T 內核原始碼感興趣，或移植某些系統到較舊的 OnePlus 設備，可前往 GitHub 獲取 OnePlus 6T 的內核原始碼。"},{"pid":"c9574d09b618d975d666715df277618b1dc93586","tid":884827,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164ed765e7177a8f5a1ba044144be30c840cc714","tid":884827,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:24:10.000Z","msg":"iOS 都有<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/apple/darwin-xnu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fapple%2Fdarwin-xnu&d=b7DOn9OyI3Miq2JAdG7N8GowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=9c025d79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/apple/darwin-xnu</a>"},{"pid":"5313ee90c2b0013889ede2ab66